reviewText: I bought this for my mother thinkingit would bejust another thing she only wants to have and not use. Well she tried it, and I got a good laugh. Worth the money!

I just had to share how much I love these DVDS. They really are worth every penny. This is the most fun I have ever had working out and boy do you get a workout! I was hooked by the time I finished the step-by-step, which btw works up a decent sweat on its own. I am no dancer by any means but these routines are easy to follow with a little practice and they are a blast! I reccomend this set to anyone looking for a fun and effective workout.
